_sText:
**Map description:**
====================
this map is a medium sized space prison full of secrets and hidden weapons.

also there is a hidden lightsaber (can you find it?).

i have also tried to give the map a more prison-like atmopshere, 
so you will not find many minigames here.

the map has 48 spawns (20 for CT and 28 for T).

those eye scanners can only be used by CTs (dont bother to try it as T).

**Features:**
==================
- low gravity football
- pool
- hidden library with a special secret in it
- hydrocultur room
- galley(kitchen) with a fridge
- healing chamber
- disco
- restroom
- and more
